{
  "stem": "4189.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so bad that when the American soldiers came in, I was asking my friends, who are these guards that are going to guard us now?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't realize that these were our liberators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the American army, of course, took the sick people out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took the sick ones out first from the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us Weimar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Weimar is the town next to Buchenwald, the closest town next to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put this up in hospitals where the-- German hospitals-- where the doctors-- they had real doctors and nurses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put us up in clean beds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took care of us in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were very fortunate that we were taken out and put into these hospitals, because the other people that were, that were a little better off that could walk, many of those people-- thousands of them, I would say-- died after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the soldiers that came in, they wanted to help us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't know, they didn't realize, that we could not eat regular food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there were giving us all their food, their rations-- sausages, butter, and all the rations that they had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the prisoners that were so many years in that camp could not digest that kind of food because all their intestines were dried up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we that were in the hospital, the doctors, they realized this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they did not give us food right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us very little food, special food that they made for us, like cereal cooked with skim milk and water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And slowly, every day, they gave us a little better food till finally, we were able to eat normal food.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
